commit.message: correct error in naming and renumbering 10-page chunks of images.
Attempting some GraphicsMagick / GhostScript memory and disk usage optimizations.
be more aggressive about using temp directories for every MAGICK_TEMPDIR call.
use the MAGICK_TMPDIR environment variable for all 'gm' calls.
forcing graphicsmagick to always observe strict memory limits, even for generating tiffs for OCR.
Adding explicit runtime dependency checking, warning, and fallback behavior for non-ocr text extraction.
Adding transparent OCR via Tesseract to Docsplit, with per-page checks and --ocr and --no-ocr flags to force it.
Refactoring the text_extractor in anticipation of OCR.
Get all of the tests passing again, and a rake task for starting openoffice.
tweaking the unsharp to be as close to the original as possible
draft of removing nearly all java dependencies in favor of poppler and pdftk
